**********************************************************************
Vdd vdd 0 1.8
Vss vss 0 0
Vctrl vctrl 0 {vctrl_val}
.PARAM vctrl_val = 0.9

Xvco outp outn vctrl vdd vss kestrel_vco

Cload_p outp 0 10f
Cload_n outn 0 10f
Ediff diff 0 outp outn 1.0
